{
  "stem": "18258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 158.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And that happened Monday after they had taken over on Friday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in our store [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] getting ready for the regular Saturday-- or Friday night and Saturday business when we heard that on the-- on the radio.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And immediately, all over the neighborhood, the, the shutters came down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The stores were closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we proceeded in all speed to remove the, the posters from our windows, which had said, vote against the Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was Friday night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night, we then sat in a neighbor's apartment, listening to-- he had a large radio.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he got some foreign stations.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were Czech citizens, so they were not immediately endangered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we listened to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was constantly funeral music and a repeat of Schuschnigg's address, and the indication that the German are on the march, and had invaded already the northern provinces of Austria-- were on their march to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- in that way, we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were not that organized immediately that they could do that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just cleaned us out as far as money and documents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My passport was confiscated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My parents-- we had-- we had a big, iron safe where we kept nothing, just our documents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to open that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were looking for money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no money in there, too bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they just-- they just made it difficult.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, of course, immediately our windows-- our display windows on the stores were marked 'Jew' and a swastika, which prevented non-Jews and the neighborhood people from even coming into our store.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Off-- our business was finished.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just stopped for a moment because there was a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
